Hello, I am writing to express my interest in the Senior Full-Stack Developer position for your AI-powered customer support dashboard. My engineering background, with a strong focus on robotics, has provided me with extensive experience in programming and developing systems that interact with their environment in real-time.

In projects like the Integrated Compliant Arm-Wrist Robot and Throw & Catch Robots, I was responsible for simulating and programming complex systems, including developing motion and control algorithms in C++. This work involved training robots for delicate manipulation tasks and fine-tuning their behavior, which I believe offers foundational experience in developing intelligent, responsive systems.

While the specific web technologies like Next.js, TypeScript, and Supabase are not explicitly in my current toolkit, my proficiency in programming languages such as C++, Java, and HTML, combined with a strong analytical approach from my engineering background, demonstrates my capacity to quickly master new technical stacks. My experience at Siemens also honed my ability to understand complex processes and documentation.

I am eager to discuss how my proven ability to program, develop real-time control systems, and quickly adapt to new technical challenges can contribute to your project. Please let me know if you would be available for a brief call to explore this further.
